Pig and Khao, with its open kitchen, is a vibrant restaurant which does not cost an arm and a leg. The food is very sophisticated, creative and, more importantly, extremely delicious. It is evident that much thought and intelligence went into every dish bringing Filipino and Thai food to a whole new level. Pig and Khao is an excellent culinary experience. Talk about getting the most bang for your buck! Check it out for yourself and you will see what I mean. And have fun.
